    <title>MarkDown语法总结</title>
    <link href="https://52yyl.github.io/2018/05/21/001-MarkDown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93-%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%E7%AF%87/"/>
    <id>https://52yyl.github.io/2018/05/21/001-MarkDown语法总结-入门篇/</id>
    <published>2018-05-21T13:12:26.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-06-01T14:30:26.014Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js"> </script><p>Markdown是一种轻量级的『标记语言』，用简洁的语法代替排版。其不追求大而全,只追求易读易写,其简洁的语法成为广受码农欢迎的网络语言.<a id="more"></a><br>    本篇介绍Markdown基本语法，内容很少，学会后可轻松写出高大上的文档，再也不需要各种编辑器去调文章格式。另外，网上有各平台下的Markdown工具可用，也有在线的，我比较习惯用sublime搞定，Markdown本来就是为了追求简洁，弄个工具岂不多此一举。下面看一些与HTML标签相对应的语法.</p><pre><code>- 标题语法与对应的html标题标签<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>      #1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>      ##2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h3</span>&gt;</span>3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h3</span>&gt;</span>      ###3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h4</span>&gt;</span>4<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h4</span>&gt;</span>      ####4</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h5</span>&gt;</span>5<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h5</span>&gt;</span>      #####5</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h6</span>&gt;</span>6<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h6</span>&gt;</span>      ######6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><p><a href="">未完待续 博主要休息了</a></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;Markdown是一种轻量级的『标记语言』，用简洁的语法代替排版。其不追求大而全,只追求易读易写,其简洁的语法成为广受码农欢迎的网络语言.
    
    </summary>
    
    
